parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the electrical system can cause the vehicle to stall or shut off while driving, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The vehicle stalls or shuts off while driving
the battery warning light is illuminated
the radio and clock screen turn off and on randomly
and the car has no signs of life.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the brake system can cause the vehicle to lose motive power, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The engine compartment fire can cause serious damage to the vehicle and potentially harm the occupants.

the engine compartment is on fire

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the clutch system can cause the vehicle to lose motive power, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.

the clutch pedal sticks to the floor

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure to address safety recall issues can cause serious safety risks to the occupants and other road users.
